  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the safety and effectiveness of autologous bone marrow
      mononuclear stem cells in patients with cerebral palsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the safety and effectiveness of autologous bone marrow
      mononuclear stem cells in 40 patients with cerebral palsy at Vinmec International Hospital,
      Hanoi, Vietnam.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
